  </a>
</span>
                                        <span class="mslo-share-btn mslo-btn-email clear-fix" title="Email">
  <div class="ugc-content-wrap clearfix">
    <a href="https://my.marthastewart.com/email?node_title=The%2010%20Rules%20for%20Making%20Chicken%20Soup&mags_origin=1108110/10-rules-making-chicken-soup&mags_base=http%3A//www.marthastewart.com/&destination=http%3A//www.marthastewart.com/1108110/10-rules-making-chicken-soup&token=cceea0e0149f81f5c514fcf5c1f9c833" class="email-frame">
